title: Speedy Teriyaki Sesame Chicken and Prawns with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Basmati Rice
description: It takes less than 25 minutes to make this Speedy Teriyaki Sesame Chicken and Prawns. Widely used in Japanese barbecue dishes, teriyaki's name comes from the Japanese 'teri', meaning 'shine' and 'yaki' meaning fried or grilled.
